reviewText: that was a good movie. Japanese, martial arts fighting with a sense of humor. oh.. lots of rather graphic love seens, i wasn't expecting that part but its really good, if you like japanese modern movie's youll love this. side note, main actress really looks a lot like a young maki goto. i actually had to pause half way to google if maki had a younger sister playing in movies. she does not, girls name is yunia haga.
